Validation
.\NWAdmin.exe -o AttachDatabase -serverName "<NewSQLServerOrAlias>" -databaseName "<NintexWorkflowContentDBName>" -integrated -validateOnly

if validation is clean
.\NWAdmin.exe -o AttachDatabase -serverName "<NewSQLServerOrAlias>" -databaseName "<NintexWorkflowContentDBName>" -integrated

After attaching, go to:
Central Administration
→ Nintex Administration
→ Database management
→ Nintex Workflow
→ Content databases
→ Manage

On that page, you should see a list something like this:
SharePoint Content Database              Map to Workflow Content Database
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WSS_Content_Intranet                      NintexWorkflow_Content_Intranet
WSS_Content_Projects                      NintexWorkflow_Content_Projects
WSS_Content_HR                            NintexWorkflow_Content_HR


